data.description: Here is your opportunity to purchase a quaint and affordable home in Kingsburg with pool. Just a few steps away from Kingsburg High School, this home has so much to offer. A large living area with fireplace. Kitchen with laminate flooring also has granite counter tops, gas range, microwave, dining area plus glass French door to patio. Tile floors are in entry, hallway and bathrooms. Hall bath has a tub shower combo as well as granite countertop. Large master bedroom with bath has a two-sink vanity plus a French door to pool area for convenience. Lots of fencing in backyard for your backyard needs. Pool is fenced separately from patio and additional fencing in backyard area for pets. A laundry room is located off the patio with sink. The pool equipment, is also located in a room off patio. Both rooms conveniently located. The garage is tucked away behind the home. You enter the garage from a front driveway leading to the back. There are two Solar systems on the home. One is owned and the other is a power purchase agreement. Perfect to keep your utilities under control.
